data.description: Bring your RV and/or BOAT and discover luxury living near Gemini Springs Park in DeBary with NO HOA! This fully remodeled 2-bed, 1-bath home boasts high-end finishes, spacious bedrooms, and a modern kitchen complete with a waterfall granite island. Nature lovers will enjoy the hiking and biking trails, playground, and springs, just a stones throw away. The backyard is enormous, featuring a fire pit, tall trees and partial fencing. Plus, the expansive side yard easily accommodates RV, boat, or trailer parking. HVAC 2014, Metal roof 2015, Water heater 2020. Don't miss the chance to own this perfect blend of elegance and outdoor bliss. Schedule a showing today!
